{"title":"Pytorch","uid":"61251d8b73997ae6479adce2ddc93d34","slug":"AI/Pytorch","date":"2022-01-01T03:39:04.000Z","updated":"2022-06-11T15:26:40.139Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/AI/Pytorch.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/img/pytorch.jpeg","content":"<h2 id=\"基于Pytorch的LSTM\"><a href=\"#基于Pytorch的LSTM\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"基于Pytorch的LSTM\"></a>基于Pytorch的LSTM</h2><h3 id=\"lstm-nn-LSTM-input-size-hidden-size-num-layers\"><a href=\"#lstm-nn-LSTM-input-size-hidden-size-num-layers\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"lstm=nn.LSTM(input_size, hidden_size, num_layers)\"></a>lstm=nn.LSTM(input_size, hidden_size, num_layers)</h3><ul>\n<li>input_size：输入的特征维度</li>\n<li>hidden_size：隐藏层的特征维度（即输出的特征维度）</li>\n<li>num_layers：LSTM隐层的层数,默认为1</li>\n<li>bias： 用不用偏置，default=True </li>\n<li>batch_first：True则输入输出的数据格式为 (batch, seq, feature)</li>\n<li>dropout：除最后一层，每一层的输出都进行dropout，默认 0</li>\n<li>bidirectional：True则为双向LSTM，默认为False</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"out-h-n-c-n-lstm-x-h-0-c-0\"><a href=\"#out-h-n-c-n-lstm-x-h-0-c-0\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"out,(h_n,c_n)= lstm(x, [h_0, c_0])\"></a>out,(h_n,c_n)= lstm(x, [h_0, c_0])</h3><ul>\n<li>x = [seq_len, batch, input_size]</li>\n<li>out = [batch_size, seq_len, directions*hidden_size],包含最后一时间步的输出特征</li>\n<li>h/c = [num_layers * directions , batch, hidden_size]</li>\n<li>$h_n$包含句子的最后一个时间步的隐藏状态，$c_n$包含最后一个单词的细胞状态，都与seq_length无关</li>\n<li>output[-1]与$h_n$是相等的，注意LSTM中的隐藏状态其实就是输出，cell state才是一直隐藏记录着信息</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Yveltals/Picgo/lstm.png\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"实例\"><a href=\"#实例\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"实例\"></a>实例</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> torch<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>nn <span class=\"token keyword\">as</span> nn\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> torch\nx <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> torch<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>rand<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">24</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">10</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">100</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># 轮数 序列长 特征维度</span>\nlstm <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> nn<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>LSTM<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>input_size<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">100</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>hidden_size<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">16</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>num_layers<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>batch_first<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token boolean\">True</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\noutput<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>h<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>c<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> lstm<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># 所有时间步的隐层结果 最后的隐藏、细胞状态</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>output<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>size<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>h<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>size<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span>\ntorch<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Size<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">24</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">10</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">16</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\ntorch<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Size<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">24</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">16</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"Anaconda使用\"><a href=\"#Anaconda使用\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Anaconda使用\"></a>Anaconda使用</h2><h3 id=\"1-环境管理\"><a href=\"#1-环境管理\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1. 环境管理\"></a>1. 环境管理</h3><ul>\n<li>查看环境</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">conda info -e\npython -V<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<ul>\n<li>创建环境</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token comment\"># 创建一个环境名为py34，指定Python版本是3.4</span>\nconda create --name py34 <span class=\"token assign-left variable\">python</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">3.4</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<ul>\n<li>激活环境</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token comment\"># 在windows环境</span>\nactivate py34\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 在Linux &amp; Mac中</span>\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">source</span> activate py34<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<ul>\n<li>退出环境</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token comment\"># 在windows环境</span>\ndeactivate\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 在Linux &amp; Mac中</span>\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">source</span> deactivate<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<ul>\n<li>删除环境</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-text\" data-language=\"text\"><code class=\"language-text\">conda remove -n py34 --all<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<h3 id=\"2-包管理\"><a href=\"#2-包管理\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2. 包管理\"></a>2. 包管理</h3><ul>\n<li>换镜像</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">conda config --add channels https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/anaconda/pkgs/free/\nconda config --add channels https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/anaconda/pkgs/main/\nconda config --set show_channel_urls <span class=\"token function\">yes</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>进入指定的环境中进行包的安装，以pandas包为例</p></blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>相关操作命令</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token comment\">#查看已安装</span>\nconda list\n<span class=\"token comment\">#检查包是否可以安装</span>\nconda search pandas\n<span class=\"token comment\">#安装更新卸载</span>\nconda <span class=\"token function\">install</span> pandas\nconda update pandas\nconda remove pandas<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<ul>\n<li>使用conda来管理conda和python的版本( 都视为包 )</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">conda update conda\nconda update anaconda\n<span class=\"token comment\">#更新python为本系列最新版本</span>\nconda update python<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"立即生效环境变量\"><a href=\"#立即生效环境变量\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"立即生效环境变量\"></a>立即生效环境变量</h2><p><strong>Win10</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">set</span> <span class=\"token assign-left variable\"><span class=\"token environment constant\">PATH</span></span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span>C\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 重启cmd</span>\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">echo</span> %<span class=\"token environment constant\">PATH</span>%<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>Ubuntu</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token comment\"># 对应相应文件</span>\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">source</span> /etc/profile<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span></sp